{"tid":2377195,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"播道會擁8億九龍塘靚地 牧師叫教友借錢還3億債","createTime":"2021-01-23T11:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T16:17:05.000Z","uid":44209,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"341a7d31a0290ee9e88e5c03787d637c56190166","tid":2377195,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》調查發現，香港基督教播道會聯會賬目混亂，2018年財務報表聲稱現金結餘只有44萬元，同年斥資3.2億元購入港大校舍作神學院用途。近月高層發公開信，指買校舍衍生赤字高達3.8億元，每月支付銀行60萬元利息，呼籲教友提供無息貸款或無償奉獻協助還債。不過，聯會實際家底豐厚，擁有3幅九龍塘地皮，共值近8億元。<br />\n<br />\n根據稅務局資料，聯會在1957年成立，登記成為慈善團體，有67個附屬機構，包括恩泉堂、同福堂、雅斤堂和播道神學院等。翻查2019年財務報表，聯會主席是蘇振豪，而社聯公開資料顯示，副主席是陳黔開牧師。<strong><span class=\"red\">陳黔開</span></strong>亦同時擔任多個基督教團體的顧問，包括城市睦福團契、基督教互愛中心，及<strong><span class=\"red\">警隊「以諾團契」</span></strong>等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vviu5Gy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvviu5Gy.png&h=9d27e24d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210123/IHB7LH7I4BB6ZK2LTKRNNVPBLE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210123%2FIHB7LH7I4BB6ZK2LTKRNNVPBLE%2F&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TalFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=c1d5d8c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210123%2FIHB7LH7I4BB6ZK2LTKRNNVPBLE%2F&h=04b078ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210123/IHB7LH7I4BB6ZK2LTKRNNVPBLE/</a>"},{"pid":"2543c955b9fcc3a400b68b9f79590a2cc07e3b40","tid":2377195,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60192ccc906d25e1228ed517873851f6e155643","tid":2377195,"uid":335434,"like":28,"dislike":0,"s